<h1 class="sectionedit1" id="cover_thumbnailer">Cover thumbnailer</h1>
<div class="level1">

<p>
Cover thumbnailer est un petit script développé en Python qui permet d&#039;afficher les pochettes des albums de musique dans nautilus, de prévisualiser les images contenues dans un dossier et plus encore.
</p>

<p>
Le script s&#039;intègre dans nautilus comme n&#039;importe quel autre thumbnailer de la GNOME thumbnail factory; vous n&#039;aurez donc pas à le lancer manuellement pour générer les miniatures.
</p>

<p>
<a href="http://doc.ubuntu-fr.org/lib/exe/fetch.php?tok=a2855f&amp;media=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.flogisoft.com%2Fubuntu-fr%2Fcover-thumbnailer_demo.jpg" class="media" title="http://static.flogisoft.com/ubuntu-fr/cover-thumbnailer_demo.jpg"><img src="http://doc.ubuntu-fr.org/lib/exe/fetch.php?tok=a2855f&amp;media=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.flogisoft.com%2Fubuntu-fr%2Fcover-thumbnailer_demo.jpg" class="mediacenter" title="cover-thumbnailer_demo.jpg" alt="cover-thumbnailer_demo.jpg" /></a>
</p>

</div>
<div class='secedit editbutton_section editbutton_1'><form class="button btn_secedit" method="post" action="cover-thumbnailer"><div class="no"><input type="hidden" name="do" value="edit" /><input type="hidden" name="rev" value="1323958632" /><input type="hidden" name="summary" value="[Cover thumbnailer] " /><input type="hidden" name="target" value="section" /><input type="hidden" name="range" value="50-543" /><input type="submit" value="Modifier" class="button" title="Cover thumbnailer" /></div></form></div>
<h2 class="sectionedit2" id="pre-requis">Pré-requis</h2>
<div class="level2">
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Disposer des <a href="sudo" class="wikilink1" title="sudo">droits d&#039;administration</a>.</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> Disposer d&#039;une connexion à Internet configurée et activée.</div>
</li>
</ul>

</div>
<div class='secedit editbutton_section editbutton_2'><form class="button btn_secedit" method="post" action="cover-thumbnailer"><div class="no"><input type="hidden" name="do" value="edit" /><input type="hidden" name="rev" value="1323958632" /><input type="hidden" name="summary" value="[Pré-requis] " /><input type="hidden" name="target" value="section" /><input type="hidden" name="range" value="544-687" /><input type="submit" value="Modifier" class="button" title="Pré-requis" /></div></form></div>
<h2 class="sectionedit3" id="installation">Installation</h2>
<div class="level2">

</div>
<div class='secedit editbutton_section editbutton_3'><form class="button btn_secedit" method="post" action="cover-thumbnailer"><div class="no"><input type="hidden" name="do" value="edit" /><input type="hidden" name="rev" value="1323958632" /><input type="hidden" name="summary" value="[Installation] " /><input type="hidden" name="target" value="section" /><input type="hidden" name="range" value="688-713" /><input type="submit" value="Modifier" class="button" title="Installation" /></div></form></div>
<h3 class="sectionedit4" id="ubuntu_910_1004_lts_1010_et_1104">Ubuntu 9.10, 10.04 LTS, 10.10 et 11.04</h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>
Pour installer Cover Thumbnailer, <a href="ppa" class="wikilink1" title="ppa">ajoutez le PPA</a> <strong>ppa:flozz/flozz</strong><sup><a href="cover-thumbnailer#fn__1" id="fnt__1" class="fn_top">1)</a></sup> dans vos sources de logiciels, puis <a href="http://doc.ubuntu-fr.org/tutoriel/comment_modifier_sources_maj#recharger_la_liste_des_paquets" class="wikilink1" title="tutoriel:comment_modifier_sources_maj">rechargez la liste des paquets</a>.
</p>

<p>
Enfin, <a href="tutoriel/comment_installer_un_paquet" class="wikilink1" title="tutoriel:comment_installer_un_paquet">installer le paquet</a> <strong><a href="apt://cover-thumbnailer" class="urlextern" title="apt://cover-thumbnailer"  rel="nofollow">cover-thumbnailer</a></strong>.
</p>

</div>
<div class='secedit editbutton_section editbutton_4'><form class="button btn_secedit" method="post" action="cover-thumbnailer"><div class="no"><input type="hidden" name="do" value="edit" /><input type="hidden" name="rev" value="1323958632" /><input type="hidden" name="summary" value="[Ubuntu 9.10, 10.04 LTS, 10.10 et 11.04] " /><input type="hidden" name="target" value="section" /><input type="hidden" name="range" value="714-1151" /><input type="submit" value="Modifier" class="button" title="Ubuntu 9.10, 10.04 LTS, 10.10 et 11.04" /></div></form></div>
<h3 class="sectionedit5" id="anciennes_versions_d_ubuntu">Anciennes versions d&#039;Ubuntu</h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>
Pour installer Cover thumbnailer sur d&#039;anciennes versions d&#039;Ubuntu, il faut récupérer le paquet debian ici :
</p>

<p>
<a href="http://software.flogisoft.com/cover-thumbnailer/fr/#telechargement" class="urlextern" title="http://software.flogisoft.com/cover-thumbnailer/fr/#telechargement"  rel="nofollow">Page de téléchargement de Cover thumbnailer</a>.
</p>

<p>
Puis <a href="tutoriel/comment_installer_un_paquet" class="wikilink1" title="tutoriel:comment_installer_un_paquet">installer le paquet</a>  <strong>cover-thumbnailer_x.x_all</strong> précédemment téléchargé.
</p>

<p>
<p><div class="noteclassic">
Nautilus doit être relancé pour que Cover thumbnailer puisse commencer son travail :
</p>
<pre class="code">nautilus -q &amp;&amp; nautilus &amp; exit</pre>

<p>

</div></p>
</p>

</div>
<div class='secedit editbutton_section editbutton_5'><form class="button btn_secedit" method="post" action="cover-thumbnailer"><div class="no"><input type="hidden" name="do" value="edit" /><input type="hidden" name="rev" value="1323958632" /><input type="hidden" name="summary" value="[Anciennes versions d'Ubuntu] " /><input type="hidden" name="target" value="section" /><input type="hidden" name="range" value="1152-1697" /><input type="submit" value="Modifier" class="button" title="Anciennes versions d'Ubuntu" /></div></form></div>
<h2 class="sectionedit6" id="configuration">Configuration</h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Pour configurer Cover Thumbnailer, il suffit d&#039;utiliser l&#039;outil de configuration graphique disponible via le menu : <strong>&quot;Système → Préférences → Cover Thumbnailer&quot;</strong>
<a href="http://doc.ubuntu-fr.org/lib/exe/fetch.php?tok=6bd7ad&amp;media=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.flogisoft.com%2Fubuntu-fr%2Fcover-thumbnailer-gui_v0.6.png" class="media" title="http://static.flogisoft.com/ubuntu-fr/cover-thumbnailer-gui_v0.6.png"><img src="http://doc.ubuntu-fr.org/lib/exe/fetch.php?tok=6bd7ad&amp;media=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.flogisoft.com%2Fubuntu-fr%2Fcover-thumbnailer-gui_v0.6.png" class="mediacenter" alt="" /></a>
</p>

</div>
<div class='secedit editbutton_section editbutton_6'><form class="button btn_secedit" method="post" action="cover-thumbnailer"><div class="no"><input type="hidden" name="do" value="edit" /><input type="hidden" name="rev" value="1323958632" /><input type="hidden" name="summary" value="[Configuration] " /><input type="hidden" name="target" value="section" /><input type="hidden" name="range" value="1698-1971" /><input type="submit" value="Modifier" class="button" title="Configuration" /></div></form></div>
<h2 class="sectionedit7" id="utilisation">Utilisation</h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
L&#039;utilisation détaillée est disponible sur la page du projet : <a href="http://software.flogisoft.com/cover-thumbnailer/fr/#utilisation" class="urlextern" title="http://software.flogisoft.com/cover-thumbnailer/fr/#utilisation"  rel="nofollow">Utilisation de Cover-thumbnailer</a>.
</p>

</div>
<div class='secedit editbutton_section editbutton_7'><form class="button btn_secedit" method="post" action="cover-thumbnailer"><div class="no"><input type="hidden" name="do" value="edit" /><input type="hidden" name="rev" value="1323958632" /><input type="hidden" name="summary" value="[Utilisation] " /><input type="hidden" name="target" value="section" /><input type="hidden" name="range" value="1972-2164" /><input type="submit" value="Modifier" class="button" title="Utilisation" /></div></form></div>
<h2 class="sectionedit8" id="problemes">Problèmes</h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Si les miniatures ne se font pas malgré avoir relancé nautilus, vérifier que la vue des dossiers soit bien en icônes.
</p>

<p>
Si cela ne fonctionne toujours pas, lancer cette commande dans un terminal :
</p>
<pre class="code">sudo gconf-schemas --register cover-thumbnailer.schemas</pre>

</div>
<div class='secedit editbutton_section editbutton_8'><form class="button btn_secedit" method="post" action="cover-thumbnailer"><div class="no"><input type="hidden" name="do" value="edit" /><input type="hidden" name="rev" value="1323958632" /><input type="hidden" name="summary" value="[Problèmes] " /><input type="hidden" name="target" value="section" /><input type="hidden" name="range" value="2165-2458" /><input type="submit" value="Modifier" class="button" title="Problèmes" /></div></form></div>
<h2 class="sectionedit9" id="desinstallation">Désinstallation</h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
<a href="tutoriel/comment_supprimer_un_paquet" class="wikilink1" title="tutoriel:comment_supprimer_un_paquet">Supprimez le paquet</a> <strong>cover-thumbnailer</strong>.
</p>

<p>
<p><div class="noteclassic">
Après désinstallation, les miniatures générées restent, pour les supprimer, tapez la commande :
</p>
<pre class="code">rm -rf ~/.thumbnails/</pre>

<p>

</div></p>
</p>

</div>
